data.name: labelInstrutionsStraightThrough.Text
data.value:
Instructions:
1. Use a Standard RS-232 Straight Through Cable. 2. CHANGE your Fluke 900 RS-232 Settings to be the following BAUD RATE: 19200 STOP BITS: 1 PARITY: EVEN DATA BITS: 7 MODE: DCE CL TIMEOUT: 2 SECS

data.name: labelInstructionsNullModem.Text
data.value:
Instructions:
1. Use a NULL Modem Cable - Same cable as DATA I/O 29B Programmers. 2. CHANGE your Fluke 900 RS-232 Settings to be the following BAUD RATE: 19200 STOP BITS: 1 PARITY: EVEN DATA BITS: 7 MODE: DTE OP TIMEOUT: 2 SECS
